OL,3,CInquest jury finds baby boy given
OL,4,Cwrong dose died of natural causes
OL,6,FA jury at an inquest into the death of
OL,7,Fa six-month-old baby, who was given
OL,8,Fthe wrong dose by medical staff at
OL,9,FRoyal Hospital, found that he died of
OL,10,Fnatural causes.
OL,12,FHunter Martin was admitted to hospital
OL,13,Fwith suspected chicken pox on 4 March
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FDespite the concerns of his parents
OL,17,FJade Smith and Alex Martin, he was
OL,18,Fgiven ibuprofen and sent home.
