OL,3,CInquest jury finds baby boy given
OL,4,Cwrong dose died of natural causes
OL,6,FOvernight, Hunter's condition
OL,7,Fworsened, and he was rushed back to
OL,8,Fhospital and to a high-dependency ward.
OL,10,FHe was then diagnosed with sepsis and
OL,11,Finvasive group A streptococcal
OL,12,Fdisease. Hunter was then administered
OL,13,Fthe antibiotic drug Clindamycin.
OL,15,FThe jury heard how he was given ten
OL,16,Ftimes the dose of medication he was
OL,17,Fsupposed to be given - 940 milligrams
OL,18,Finstead of 94 milligrams.
