OL,6,FHunter was transferred to Sheffield
OL,7,FChildren's Hospital, but he died later
OL,8,Fthat day after suffering three cardiac
OL,9,Farrests.
OL,11,FAt the hearing, a statement from
OL,12,FHunter's mother Jade Smith was read
OL,13,Fout, in which she described her son as
OL,14,F"a bonnie blue-eyed angel".
OL,16,FShe also said when she took Hunter to
OL,17,Fthe hospital the second time, she told
OL,18,Fstaff his body was swollen and his
OL,19,Feyes were puffy.
