OL,3,CInquest jury finds baby boy given
OL,4,Cwrong dose died of natural causes
OL,6,FThe trust which runs Chesterfield
OL,7,FRoyal Hospital had previously admitted
OL,8,Fthere were missed opportunities to
OL,9,Fdiagnose Hunter and had Hunter been
OL,10,Fgiven the correct antibiotics earlier,
OL,11,Fon the balance of probabilities he
OL,12,Fmight have survived.
OL,14,FThey also admitted there had been an
OL,15,Ferror in the dosage of antibiotics
OL,16,Fgiven to Hunter but they are not clear
OL,17,Fwhether this contributed to the little
OL,18,Fboy's deterioration.
